{
  "stem": "3964.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] Well, they hauled him out the next morning, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] put him on the wagon like so many others, stiff as a board, and took him over to the crematorium, burned him.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I could tell you experiences like that, similar to that, numerous ones.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "But there are too many of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "Too many of them have been-- not too many.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "Many of them have been told already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "And I don't want to just be repetitious and tell them over and over again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The early part in 1945, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] as I said earlier, I seemingly had some help from other people who were in the barracks, gotten some extra food.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father was still alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And he was very sick too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "And I couldn't help him, obviously, because I couldn't even help myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "But I'd gotten stronger as I went along and my father got worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I hadn't seen my sister for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Approximately March or April-- I think it was April-- in 1945, again the Germans decided to liquidate Stutthof, because the Russians were knocking at the doors.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they took us all out into a large assembly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "And they segregated those who were capable of walking [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from those who were very sick and not capable of walking anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "I was capable of walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "They put me in one group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "And my father was not capable of standing on his feet anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "They put him in another group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they sent the people who were not capable of walking anymore back into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
